WEBVTT

00:07:58.440 --> 00:08:02.856
Thanks to the universal penetration
of running water and electricity

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:04.256
in the developed world

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:08.256
and the widespread adoption
of washing machines, vacuum cleaners,

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:12.256
refrigerators, dishwashers,
stoves and microwaves,

00:08:12.280 --> 00:08:15.176
the amount of our lives
that we forfeit to housework

00:08:15.200 --> 00:08:17.576
has fallen from 60 hours a week

00:08:17.600 --> 00:08:19.560
to fewer than 15 hours a week.

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:25.296
Do all of these gains in health,
wealth, safety, knowledge and leisure

00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:27.016
make us any happier?

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.256
The answer is yes.

00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:30.456
In 86 percent of the world's countries,